sentence: Looking at options trading activity among components of the S&P 500 index, there is noteworthy activity today in Alphabet Inc (Symbol: GOOGL), where a total volume of 11,206 contracts has been traded thus far today, a contract volume which is representative of approximately 1.1 million underlying shares (given that every 1 contract represents 100 underlying shares).
That number works out to 61.2% of GOOGL's average daily trading volume over the past month, of 1.8 million shares.
Especially high volume was seen for the $1205 strike call option expiring August 23, 2019, with 462 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 46,200 underlying shares of GOOGL.
